svg.title: A diagram of three sets of footmarks. Two sets come from the left. One set, labeled “Fordingbridge,” stops in the middle of the diagram, near a large triangular shape labeled “Wreck.” The other set of tracks, labeled “Number 2,” parallels the first set but then continues off to the right. The third set, labeled “Number 3 Light Trail,” comes from the lower right to the end of the Fordingbridge tracks. They then turn back to the right, alongside Number 2, where they are labeled “Number 3 Heavy Trail.”
